004package test;
005
006import kut.*;
007
008/** All tests. */
009public class J00all {
010  /**
011  Process a test request.
012  @param rq JSON request.
013  @return JSON response.
014  */
015  public static String process (String rq) {
016    Dic<String> mrq = Js.ro(rq);
017    String type = Js.rs(mrq.get("type"));
018    if (type.equals("test")) return Js.w(J01test.run(mrq));
019    else if (type.equals("quotes")) return Js.w(J02quotes.run(mrq));
020    else if (type.equals("volume")) return Js.w(J03volume.run(mrq));
021    else if (type.equals("refs")) return Js.w(J04refs.run(mrq));
022    else if (type.equals("stSimple")) return Js.w(J05stSimple.run(mrq));
023    else if (type.equals("stSimple2")) return Js.w(J06stSimple2.run(mrq));
024    else if (type.equals("stGroup")) return Js.w(J07stGroup.run(mrq));
025    else if (type.equals("stGroup2")) return Js.w(J08stGroup2.run(mrq));
026    else if (type.equals("stOpen")) return Js.w(J09stOpen.run(mrq));
027    else throw new RuntimeException("Test type '" + type + "' is not valid.");
028  }
029}
